dev-master.name: friendsoftypo3/cms-func
dev-master.description: Brings the backend Web->functions main module for extensions to hook in

7.6.21.name: instituteweb/typo3-cms
7.6.21.description: Fork of TYPO3 CMS with production files only. TYPO3 CMS is a free open source Content Management Framework initially created by Kasper Skaarhoj and licensed under GNU/GPL.

suggest.ext-gd: GDlib/Freetype is required for building images with text (GIFBUILDER) and can also be used to scale images
suggest.ext-fileinfo: Used for proper file type detection in the file abstraction layer
suggest.ext-zlib: TYPO3 uses zlib for amongst others output compression and un/packing t3x extension files
